{
  "stem": "23599.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then it came the time where they started-- where they started, the people where-- where they came-- the rumors that what they took-- they took away the-- they sent away the people from camps.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They sent them from the east to the west, because they were afraid they will be-- they will be caught.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And German didn't want to-- people to see that they were-- that they were working there [? and ?] [? in ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they made them walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he came to me and says, Else, do you mind if I change that pullover for a pair of shoes?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because without the pullover, with my old pullover, I can walk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But without shoes if we will have to walk, too-- at that time they were talking about that were-- when-- I'll have to walk.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I need the shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, go ahead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That is a story about the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] about the shoes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I-- I didn't have shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I got this-- the shoes there-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there we got the Dutch shoes, the wooden Dutch.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What the Dutch wear, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what I got there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Plaszow was when they took us to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a huge-- [INAUDIBLE] a huge-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] what was it?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A huge-- a lots of people who they had to-- everybody again in the morning, that was when I was dreaming about my father.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think I told you that my father said that he will save us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was still in my head in the morning-- [INAUDIBLE] in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said to my cousin, everything will be fine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We'll get out of here.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
